  "content": "<div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\"><h1 class=\"header-anchor-post\"><strong>WE ARE OFFICIALLY LIVE ON PLAY STORE AND EPIC GAMES!</strong><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"§we-are-officially-live-on-play-store-and-epic-games\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/158906558/we-are-officially-live-on-play-store-and-epic-games\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h1><p><span>You can now find Treeverse on the </span><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.EndlessClouds.Treeverse&amp;pli=1\" rel=\"\">Google Play Store (Android)</a><span> and </span><a href=\"https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/treeverse-e5df22\" rel=\"\">Epic Games (Windows)</a><span>! We are still in the process of App Store for iOS.</span></p><p>You can download now and start playing across multiple servers!</p><p>Keep in mind the reward campaign has not begun. Details on that will be provided on all of our official announcement channels ahead of time. However the build will be the same so you can get a feel of things by playing it now.</p><p>This is a major step and would love for you to share it online and talk about it. We will interact and repost all Treeverse content.</p><p>We still have so much more to build and improve: game design, fundamental progression systems, mounts, pets, guilds, main quest storyline, side quests, pvp, improved content, more dungeons/items/weapons/zones, etc... — this is your first time into the world of Treeverse so cherish this experience and witness the growth alongside us.</p><h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.EndlessClouds.Treeverse&amp;pli=1\" rel=\"\">Play Store</a><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"§play-store\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/158906558/play-store\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h2><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.EndlessClouds.Treeverse&amp;pli=1\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!2TUG!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2beb0018-3eb3-4b80-a56f-2dcf1aa2e84a_7