uot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/158906558?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c96f3b9-eeb9-4f0c-9d6b-b33c4be05156_722x274.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!6SHJ!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c96f3b9-eeb9-4f0c-9d6b-b33c4be05156_722x274.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!6SHJ!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c96f3b9-eeb9-4f0c-9d6b-b33c4be05156_722x274.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!6SHJ!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c96f3b9-eeb9-4f0c-9d6b-b33c4be05156_722x274.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!6SHJ!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7c96f3b9-eeb9-4f0c-9d6b-b33c4be05156_722x274.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><div><hr></div><p><strong>FAQ</strong></p><p><strong>Will we be rewarded for playing this game?</strong></p><p>There will be a reward campaign announced very soon so keep an eye on official announcements! There are no rewards before the campaign begins.</p><p><strong>Will the data be reset?</strong></p><p>Yes, all data will be reset before the reward campaign.</p><p><strong>Can I play this game on Mac?</strong></p><p>No. We currently support downloads on Play Store and Epic Games with App Store coming soon.</p><p><strong>Will I be able to use my NFTs in game?</strong></p><p>For the time being we do not support existing NFTs. Expect to be able to use them in future releases.</p><p><strong>I have a grey screen of death, what do I do?</strong></p><p><span>We do not support VPNs so that may be causing it. If you face any other issues, join our </span><a href=\"http://discord.gg/endlessclouds\" rel=\"\">Discord</a><span> and let us know!</span></p><p><strong>Where can I stay updated?</strong></p><p><span>Please join our </span><a href=\"http://discord.gg/endlessclouds\" rel=\"\">Discord</a><span> to be the first to hear when new announcements drop. And subscribe to our Substack.</span></p><p data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://discord.com/invite/endlessclouds&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Discord&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\" class=\"button-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://discord.com/invite/endlessclouds\" rel=\"\" class=\"button primary\"><span>Discord</span></a></p></div>"
